{"tid":1106062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】報告：美國減少從中國進口　轉向越南台灣等地採購","createTime":"2019-04-14T10:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T11:48:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"07f7a074b270e32114c1bd0c297891185e720565","tid":1106062,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】報告：美國減少從中國進口　轉向越南台灣等地採購<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/273726/%e3%80%90%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%b8%9b%e5%b0%91%e5%be%9e%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%80%b2%e5%8f%a3%e3%80%80%e8%bd%89%e5%90%91%e8%b6%8a%e5%8d%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F273726%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%25b2%25bf%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%2588%25b0%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25b8%259b%25e5%25b0%2591%25e5%25be%259e%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2580%25b2%25e5%258f%25a3%25e3%2580%2580%25e8%25bd%2589%25e5%2590%2591%25e8%25b6%258a%25e5%258d%2597%2F&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=fb844cba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/273726/%e3%80%90%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%b8%9b%e5%b0%91%e5%be%9e%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%80%b2%e5%8f%a3%e3%80%80%e8%bd%89%e5%90%91%e8%b6%8a%e5%8d%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰快將達成共識，惟兩國仍然互相加徵關稅。路透社昨日引述標準普爾旗下貿易數據公司Panjiva前日的報告指，美國轉而向越南、台灣、南韓、墨西哥等購買作為關稅目標的貨品。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，美國零售商如宜家家居（IKEA）、家得寶（Home Depot）、塔吉特（Target）等，從中國進口傢俬在首季度下降13.5%，從越南和台灣進口則分別增長37.2%和19.3%。此外，美國從中國進口冰箱下降24.1%，惟南韓和墨西哥則分別增長31.8%和32%。汽車行業亦有類似情況，從中國進口輪胎下降28.6%，而從越南和南韓進口分別增長141.7%和11.1%。<br />\n<br />\n多間海外企業面對大幅提高的關稅，考慮將工廠或生產線遷離中國大陸，包括日企三菱電機、旭化成、南韓企業LG、三星等。美國總統特朗普曾表示，即使與中國達成貿易協議，關稅亦會持續一段相當長的時間，以確保中國遵守協議。"},{"pid":"fe1534c5e212341727e7c83f0d9e3fe993329a62","tid":1106062,"uid":54733,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"越南、台灣、南韓、墨西哥成大嬴家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af22b4f01cf51bbcbd0e629b89d6b7f7a732c0b","tid":1106062,"uid":50386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"美國入口支那貨大減<br />\n但係支那官方出口數據大升<br />\n代表乜嘢？"},{"pid":"34178de57ae19688c835564ab25abfe540ef06c6","tid":1106062,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8af22b4f01cf51bbcbd0e629b89d6b7f7a732c0b","tid":1106062,"uid":50386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"美國入口支那貨大減<br />\n但係支那官方出口數據大升<br />\n代表乜嘢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"出口香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd758e4e5c8dfc31acc6f08c8444bf2417b73b83","tid":1106062,"uid":173271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfRiYOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfRiYOk.jpg&h=beba52ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05455b9041679bf7ab55c2a7d70f095b3a78c28e","tid":1106062,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1534c5e212341727e7c83f0d9e3fe993329a62","tid":1106062,"uid":54733,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"越南、台灣、南韓、墨西哥成大嬴家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf90e0c4617fccbd71bf460aa5a07c3459351a3","tid":1106062,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af22b4f01cf51bbcbd0e629b89d6b7f7a732c0b","tid":1106062,"uid":50386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"美國入口支那貨大減<br />\n但係支那官方出口數據大升<br />\n代表乜嘢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" c